description:
The request message to list related account groups.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the project to list related account groups from, in the format "projects/{project}".

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of groups to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 50 groups will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A page token, received from a previous ListRelatedAccountGroups call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to ListRelatedAccountGroups must match the call that provided the page token.
